channel.title: Episode 17 of Bootstrapped.fm - call for questions/topics
channel.description:
On the next episode of [Bootstrapped.fm][1], @ian and I will talk with special guest, @rachelandrew of Perch.
If you have any questions for Rachel or topics that you'd like us to cover, please either [let me know][2] before tomorrow (8/6/2013), or post them here, and we'll do our best to cover them on the episode.
[1]: http://bootstrapped.fm [2]: http://twitter.com/andrey_butov
